@startuml Sequence_UC15
title UC-15: Akses dan Ekspor Laporan

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "Halaman Laporan\n(livewire/laporan)" as View
participant "Laporan\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "PdfController" as PdfCtrl
participant "XXXExport\n(Maatwebsite)" as ExcelExport
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /laporan
View -> Component: mount()
Component --> View: Render form filter laporan

User -> View: Pilih jenis laporan,\nrentang tanggal, filter tambahan
View -> Component: applyFilter($type, $from, $to, $filters)
Component -> DB: SELECT ... FROM transactions/expenses/productions/hitungs\nWHERE date BETWEEN ? AND ?
DB --> Component: Data laporan
Component --> View: Render tabel & ringkasan laporan

== Ekspor PDF ==
User -> View: Klik Ekspor PDF
View -> PdfCtrl: GET /laporan/export-pdf?type=...&from=...&to=...
PdfCtrl -> DB: Query data laporan
DB --> PdfCtrl: Data
PdfCtrl -> PdfCtrl: $pdf = PDF::loadView('laporan.pdf', $data)
PdfCtrl --> User: return $pdf->download('laporan.pdf')

== Ekspor Excel ==
User -> View: Klik Ekspor Excel
View -> ExcelExport: GET /laporan/export-excel
ExcelExport -> DB: Query data sesuai filter
DB --> ExcelExport: Data
ExcelExport -> ExcelExport: Excel::download(new XxxExport($data), 'laporan.xlsx')
ExcelExport --> User: Download file Excel

@enduml
